entries.journal_entry_description: Mon Mothma congratulated you on your success.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: [Mon Mothma] I have received word of your success.  Your heroism and dedication is an inspiration to us all. The Alliance is in your debt. Please accept this token of our appreciation.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: [Cale Herron] I just heard someone infiltrated the quarantine zone and stole something Vader wanted for the Rebels. Hahaha...I wouldn't want to be that person right now.
